Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:50.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,繫緊了  快點\N{\rENG}Tie it off, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:17.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,夥計們  夥計們  我們還是回去吧\N{\rENG}Hey, guys! Guys, I think we should turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.42,0:01:19.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,放著錢不賺  休想\N{\rENG}And lose good money? Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:20.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,跟緊點\N{\rENG}Stay close.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:30.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,到了\N{\rENG}Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.86,0:01:32.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,踩他上去\N{\rENG}Get on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:53.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,快點\N{\rENG}Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:07.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,他在那裡  去抓他\N{\rENG}There he is. Go get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:09.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,我會讓你付出代價的\N{\rENG}Oh, you'll pay for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,不要  不要  求你\N{\rENG}No. No, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,求你了  不要\N{\rENG}Please, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:34.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,站住\N{\rENG}Hold it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:54.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,我只抓到一隻...\N{\rENG}I only got one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:55.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,但他是個好樣本\N{\rENG}but he's a fine specimen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,-就這點  -對\N{\rENG}- That's all? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,那蘑菇咬了我兩次\N{\rENG}That shroom bit me twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:15.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,彼岸花\N{\rENG}Tomb Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:39.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,很久很久以前\N{\rENG}Once upon a time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:42.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,很久很久以前又一次\N{\rENG}or perhaps twice upon a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:44.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們可能還記得這個故事\N{\rENG}for you may remember this story...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:48.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,有一位叫瑪琳菲森的強大仙子\N{\rENG}there was a powerful Fey named Maleficent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:56.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\fad(4000,1200)\bord0\shad1\pos(192,225.6)\c&HD8FFB0&}沉睡魔咒2：惡魔夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:00.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,出於某些原因  這位惡魔夫人\N{\rENG}For some reason, the mistress of evil
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:01.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,摩爾王國的守護者\N{\rENG}and protector of the Moors...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:04.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,過了這麼久  依舊被人憎惡\N{\rENG}was still hated after all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:07.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,的確  她對奧蘿拉公主施過咒\N{\rENG}True, she had cursed the princess, Aurora...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:09.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,但那時的她還沒有發現\N{\rENG}but that was before she found light
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,人類孩童心中的善良之光\N{\rENG}in the heart of a human child...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:14.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,也還沒有將她視如己出撫養長大\N{\rENG}and raised the girl as her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:17.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,畢竟  正是瑪琳菲森的愛\N{\rENG}After all, it was Maleficent's love
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:20.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,解開了那個詛咒\N{\rENG}which broke that very same curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:24.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,但這個細節卻不知怎地被人遺忘了\N{\rENG}But that detail was somehow mysteriously forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,而王國裡始終流傳著的\N{\rENG}For as the tale was told
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:30.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,被人一遍又一遍重復的故事\N{\rENG}over and again throughout the kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:35.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,是瑪琳菲森又一次做了惡人\N{\rENG}Maleficent became the villain once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,時候到了  來吧  把大家都叫來\N{\rENG}It's time, guys. Come on. Let's get everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:50.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,今天可是大日子\N{\rENG}It's the big day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:51.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,-來吧  -走吧\N{\rENG}- Come on. - Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:53.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,醒醒  醒醒\N{\rENG}Wake up. Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:55.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,快來呀\N{\rENG}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:09.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,快點  泥沼精  時候到了\N{\rENG}Hurry up, wallerbogs! It's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:26.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們倆還記得秘密計劃嗎\N{\rENG}Do you both remember the secret plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,全在腦袋裡呢\N{\rENG}I've got it all right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:30.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,我什麼時候把秘密告訴給女王\N{\rENG}When do I tell the queen the secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:31.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,你必須得耐心點  綠蕨仙子\N{\rENG}You must be patient, Thistlewit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們覺得奧蘿拉女王醒了嗎\N{\rENG}Do you think Queen Aurora's awake yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:36.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,反正她已經不是"睡美人"了\N{\rENG}Well, she's not "Sleeping Beauty" anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:39.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,我聽懂你這個雙關了\N{\rENG}I see what you did there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:54.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,接下來要討論的是  仙子失蹤\N{\rENG}Next item of business, the missing fairies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:57.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,我已經派出更多精靈去搜尋彼岸花園了\N{\rENG}I've sent more sprites to search the Tomb Bloom field.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,傍晚時分他們會來匯報進展\N{\rENG}They'll report back to me at nightfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:02.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,在找到他們之前我們會繼續搜尋\N{\rENG}We will keep searching until we find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:07.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,請別對我舉樹枝表達不滿  葉夫\N{\rENG}Please don't raise your roots at me, Lief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,用你的軀幹碾壓人類沒有用\N{\rENG}Crushing humans with branches is not going to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:15.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,迪瓦爾  你應該站在我這邊的\N{\rENG}Diaval, you're supposed to be on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:20.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,我是摩爾王國的女王  我就是人類\N{\rENG}Well, I'm Queen of the Moors, and I am a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:26.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們須得學會心存一點善意\N{\rENG}We must all learn a little kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:28.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,別擋道\N{\rENG}Coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:29.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,借過\N{\rENG}Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,官方精靈事務\N{\rENG}Official pixie business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:32.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,借一步說話  陛下\N{\rENG}A word, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:34.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,-或者借兩步  -姑母們\N{\rENG}- Maybe two. - Aunties...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們得跟其他人一樣等輪到自己再說\N{\rENG}you need to wait your turn like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:38.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,不行  這件事不能等  女王陛下\N{\rENG}No! This can't wait, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:39.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,片刻不容\N{\rENG}Not for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:42.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,不然我就要炸了  我真的會炸\N{\rENG}Or I might burst. Truly, I might.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,那不是...\N{\rENG}Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:48.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,賓托\N{\rENG}Pinto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,她帶了禮物來\N{\rENG}She's come bearing gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:53.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,暖樹上的第一滴樹汁\N{\rENG}The first sap from the warming trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:54.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,為了大日子準備的\N{\rENG}It's for the big day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,閉嘴  綠蕨仙子\N{\rENG}Quiet, Thistlewit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:57.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,什麼大日子\N{\rENG}What big day?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:02.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的王冠\N{\rENG}My crown!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:09.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,我沒心情陪你們逗趣\N{\rENG}I'm not in the mood for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,賓托\N{\rENG}Pinto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:23.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,行了\N{\rENG}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:26.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們要去哪裡  姑母們\N{\rENG}Where are you going, aunties?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,我沒時間跟你玩  賓托\N{\rENG}I don't have time for games, Pinto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:51.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們到底怎麼回事\N{\rENG}What's gotten into all of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,她去那邊了  陛下\N{\rENG}There she goes, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,快回來\N{\rENG}Come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:15.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,賓托  今天玩夠了吧\N{\rENG}Pinto. I've had enough of your games for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,看我成什麼樣了\N{\rENG}Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:27.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,菲力浦  你來做什麼\N{\rENG}Philip. What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:28.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,我在找你\N{\rENG}I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:29.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,-你好嗎  -你好\N{\rENG}- Oh, well, hello. - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:32.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉  我現在沒空跟你聊天\N{\rENG}I'm really sorry, I can't talk right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:34.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,摩爾王國一片混亂\N{\rENG}The Moors have turned to madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,我有一大堆投訴要處理\N{\rENG}I've got a castle full of complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:36.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道你有多忙\N{\rENG}I know how busy you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:39.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,我本想問你件事\N{\rENG}I wanted to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:39.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,問吧\N{\rENG}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:43.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,你覺得奧斯戴王國和摩爾王國有可能結盟嗎\N{\rENG}Do you think there could be a union between Ulstead and the Moors?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:45.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,結盟\N{\rENG}A union?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:47.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,將兩地連接起來\N{\rENG}To connect both lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:50.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,帶來和諧與和平\N{\rENG}To bring harmony and peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:52.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想可以架起一座橋\N{\rENG}I've been imagining a bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:54.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,一座橋\N{\rENG}Oh, a bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:55.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒錯  一座橋\N{\rENG}Yes, a bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,結盟是個好主意...\N{\rENG}A union's a wonderful idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:00.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果雙方同意的話\N{\rENG}if both sides are willing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:04.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,這個嘛  我正在努力\N{\rENG}Well, I'm working on that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:05.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,他要搞砸了\N{\rENG}He's going to blow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:07.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,給他點時間  他還在熱身\N{\rENG}Give him time. He's warming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:10.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\rENG}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,你今天穿得好正式\N{\rENG}That's your formal coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們都有份參與  對吧\N{\rENG}You're in on all of this, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果你忙的話  我可以之後再來\N{\rENG}If you're busy, I could always come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:22.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,不不  不用\N{\rENG}No. No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:24.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,我完全不忙\N{\rENG}I'm not busy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:25.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,可是我不想...\N{\rENG}No, because I'd hate to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:27.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,真的  我有空\N{\rENG}Really. All ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:28.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,你想說什麼\N{\rENG}What did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:31.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,你說得對  他要搞砸了\N{\rENG}You're right. He's blowing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,五年前  我以為自己永遠失去你了\N{\rENG}Five years ago, I thought I lost you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:39.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,我決定改變這一天的意義\N{\rENG}I've decided to reclaim this day for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:42.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,我對你一見鐘情\N{\rENG}I've loved you since the moment I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:43.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,日漸情深\N{\rENG}and every day since.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果世間有真愛  那我找到了\N{\rENG}If love has a truth, here is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:48.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒有任何魔法或詛咒\N{\rENG}There is no magic nor curse
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,能把我從你身邊分開  奧蘿拉\N{\rENG}that could ever tear me away from you, Aurora.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,你確定現在方便嗎\N{\rENG}Are you sure this is a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:57.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,菲力浦\N{\rENG}Oh, Philip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:00.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,他跪下了\N{\rENG}He's on his knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:03.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,他可真夠磨蹭的\N{\rENG}He took his sweet time about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:05.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,你願意嫁給我嗎\N{\rENG}Will you marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:08.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,我願意\N{\rENG}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:10.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,-願意  -願意\N{\rENG}- Yes? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:13.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,我願意  快起來吻我\N{\rENG}Yes! Yes, just stand up. Kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:25.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們要辦婚禮了\N{\rENG}We're having a wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:29.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,秘密驚喜婚禮\N{\rENG}A secret surprise wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,當然了  我們要告訴雙方家長\N{\rENG}Of course, we have to tell our parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:39.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,一定要嗎\N{\rENG}Do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:11.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,夫人\N{\rENG}Mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:12.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,什麼事\N{\rENG}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:14.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,我有個消息\N{\rENG}I have a little bit of news.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:16.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,那就說吧\N{\rENG}Well, on with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:20.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,不是什麼大事\N{\rENG}It's nothing of any real consequence...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:23.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,絕對不必反應過激\N{\rENG}and it's certainly no reason to overreact.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:25.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,只不過是\N{\rENG}It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:29.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,菲力浦王子...\N{\rENG}Prince Philip has, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,失蹤了\N{\rENG}Disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,不是  菲力浦...\N{\rENG}No. No. Philip has...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:35.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,染上黃熱病了  不  等等\N{\rENG}Yellow fever? No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:37.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,得麻風病了\N{\rENG}Leprosy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:39.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,不是  夫人\N{\rENG}No, Mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:43.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,菲力浦王子向奧蘿拉求...\N{\rENG}Prince Philip has asked Aurora if she'll become his...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:44.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\rENG}Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:47.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,毀了我的早晨\N{\rENG}ruin my morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:51.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,夫人  拜託\N{\rENG}Mistress, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:56.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,冷靜點\N{\rENG}Stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:05.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,告訴我  殿下\N{\rENG}So, tell me, sire...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,我要當伴郎嗎\N{\rENG}am I to be a best man,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:09.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,還是說您從摩爾找了個怪物伴郎\N{\rENG}or did you choose a creature from the Moors?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:11.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,將軍  如果你想打聽\N{\rENG}General, if that's your way of asking me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:12.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,她有沒有答應\N{\rENG}if she said yes, then I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:14.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道她答應了  殿下\N{\rENG}I know she said yes, sire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,哪個人類不想離開那個鬼地方\N{\rENG}What human wouldn't want to leave that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:19.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,你對摩爾居民有什麼不滿嗎  珀西瓦爾\N{\rENG}What do you have against Moor folk, Percival?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:21.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,"摩爾居民"  要這麼稱呼他們嗎\N{\rENG}"Moor folk"? Is that what we're calling them now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:24.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,長翅膀的野獸  兇殘的樹木\N{\rENG}Winged beasts, murderous trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,注意言辭  將軍\N{\rENG}Guard your tongue, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:27.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,你對他們一無所知\N{\rENG}You know nothing about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道瑪琳菲森殺人如麻\N{\rENG}I know that Maleficent is a killer of men...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:32.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,毀滅軍隊  故事大家都知道\N{\rENG}destroyer of armies. Or so the story goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:35.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,她不是那樣的\N{\rENG}She's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:37.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,保護這個王國是我的職責\N{\rENG}It's my job to protect this kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:40.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,老朋友  我會盡職盡責\N{\rENG}And I will do so, old friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:42.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,毫不猶豫\N{\rENG}without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:44.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\rENG}Walk on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:51.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,開門\N{\rENG}Open the gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:52.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,開門\N{\rENG}Open the gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:03.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,陛下  吞併中部的\N{\rENG}Your Majesty, spoils from the annexation
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:04.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,戰利品送達了\N{\rENG}of the Midlands have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:06.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,是武器\N{\rENG}Weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:10.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,不  我們不需要武器\N{\rENG}No. We have no need of arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們征戰的日子結束了\N{\rENG}Our days of war are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:17.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,英格瑞斯\N{\rENG}Ingrith...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,看到我給你留的位置了吧\N{\rENG}you see where I've had you placed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,就在我身後\N{\rENG}Right behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:25.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,我永遠都會在你身後\N{\rENG}And that's where I'll always be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:28.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,英格瑞斯  我說了不需要武器\N{\rENG}Ingrith, I said we had no need of arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,有備無患\N{\rENG}One can never be too careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:39.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,陛下  弩上弦了\N{\rENG}Your Majesty, it's cocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:41.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,是嗎\N{\rENG}Is it, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:48.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,-父親  母親  -怎麼樣\N{\rENG}- Father, Mother. - Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,她怎麼說\N{\rENG}What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:52.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,她答應了\N{\rENG}She said yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:53.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\rENG}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:56.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,真是天大的好消息\N{\rENG}That is wonderful news.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:15:00.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,兩個王國終於團結一致了\N{\rENG}Two kingdoms united at last. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:05.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\rENG}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:08.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,也許我太自私了\N{\rENG}Perhaps I've been selfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,對此事的看法有錯\N{\rENG}looking at this the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,你已經做出了選擇\N{\rENG}You've made your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:16.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,現在該慶祝了\N{\rENG}Now is a time to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:22.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,很高興你終於認可了\N{\rENG}I'm glad you finally approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:23.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,不僅如此\N{\rENG}Much more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:28.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,我準備熱情歡迎你的未婚妻\N{\rENG}I am ready to welcome your fiancee with open arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:31.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,她要來參加晚宴\N{\rENG}She shall come to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:32.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,那太好了\N{\rENG}That would be incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:34.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,但有一個條件\N{\rENG}Under one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:36.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,她要帶上她的教母\N{\rENG}She will bring her godmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:37.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,陛下  我強烈...\N{\rENG}Your Majesty, I strongly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:39.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們要在這座城堡裡\N{\rENG}We will meet the one who raised her
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.74,0:15:41.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,見一見養育她的教母\N{\rENG}right here in this castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒錯  王后說得對\N{\rENG}Yes. The queen is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:44.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不確定她的教母會不會...\N{\rENG}I'm not sure her godmother will...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:46.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,我堅持如此\N{\rENG}No, but I insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:49.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,畢竟  我們馬上就要成為一家人了\N{\rENG}After all, we will soon be family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:52.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,通知全國上下\N{\rENG}Well, let it be known throughout the kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:56.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,我兒子要娶奧蘿拉了\N{\rENG}that my son is to marry Aurora.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:16:00.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,並且瑪琳菲森要來參加晚宴\N{\rENG}And Maleficent is coming to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:04.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,我馬上傳話下去\N{\rENG}I shall send word straightaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,來了\N{\rENG}Incoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:34.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,抓住裙子別放\N{\rENG}Hold on to your petticoats!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:46.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,看啊\N{\rENG}Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:50.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣\N{\rENG}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:52.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣\N{\rENG}So.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:57.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,教母\N{\rENG}Godmother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:03.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,菲力浦向我求婚了\N{\rENG}Philip asked me to marry him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:06.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,真可憐\N{\rENG}Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:07.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,他會緩過來的\N{\rENG}He'll recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:11.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,我答應他了\N{\rENG}My answer was yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:17.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,-不行  -行\N{\rENG}- No. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:19.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,我沒有徵求你的意見\N{\rENG}I wasn't really asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:20.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,我也沒有\N{\rENG}Nor was I.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:22.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,你要怎麼做\N{\rENG}What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:24.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,把他變成山羊嗎\N{\rENG}You'll turn him into a goat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:27.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,別鬧了\N{\rENG}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,你為什麼不喜歡菲力浦\N{\rENG}Why don't you like Philip?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:33.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,首先  他是人類\N{\rENG}Well, for one thing, he's human.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,我也是人類\N{\rENG}I'm a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:38.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,我從沒因為這點而針對過你\N{\rENG}And I have never held that against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:39.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,直到我墜入愛河\N{\rENG}Until I fell in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:44.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,愛情未必會結局圓滿  小怪物\N{\rENG}Love doesn't always end well, Beasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:48.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,你要知道菲力浦可是一位王子\N{\rENG}I'll have you know Prince Philip is a prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:51.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,一位非常英俊有魅力的王子\N{\rENG}A very handsome and charming prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,求求你相信我\N{\rENG}I'm just asking you to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:17:59.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,給他一個機會\N{\rENG}Please give him a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:01.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,讓我們證明你是錯的\N{\rENG}Let us prove you wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:03.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,菲力浦很善良\N{\rENG}Philip is thoughtful...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:05.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,很體貼\N{\rENG}he's very kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:06.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,體什麼\N{\rENG}Kind of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,國王和王后邀請我們母女\N{\rENG}The king and queen are celebrating tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:12.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,今晚去城堡參加慶祝晚宴\N{\rENG}and they have invited both of us to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:17.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,你想讓我見他父母\N{\rENG}You want me to meet his parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:18.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,只是頓晚餐而已\N{\rENG}It's just a dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:23.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,奧斯戴王國不歡迎我\N{\rENG}They don't want me in Ulstead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:25.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,為什麼我還要去\N{\rENG}Why on earth would I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:27.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,因為他母親想見一見我母親\N{\rENG}Because his mother wishes to meet mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:31.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\rENG}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:40.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,菲力浦\N{\rENG}Philip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:43.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想讓你今晚佩戴這個\N{\rENG}I want you to wear this tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:45.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,你的寶劍\N{\rENG}Your sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:47.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,因為你的緣故\N{\rENG}Because of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:50.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,奧斯戴王國和摩爾王國終於可以團結一致\N{\rENG}Ulstead and the Moors will be united at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:56.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,父親  我對奧蘿拉的愛不夾雜任何政治因素\N{\rENG}Father, my love for Aurora has nothing to do with politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:58.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒錯  但你們的愛情\N{\rENG}Yes, but your love...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:02.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,可以確保世世代代和平共處\N{\rENG}will ensure peace for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:05.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,拿著它  佩戴上\N{\rENG}Now take it. And wear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,提醒自己我們再也無需兵戎相見\N{\rENG}to know that you will never have to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:11.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的孩子\N{\rENG}Oh, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:14.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,我從未感到如此自豪\N{\rENG}I've never been more proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,母親那邊怎麼樣\N{\rENG}And what about Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:20.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,她能接受嗎\N{\rENG}Is she okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:25.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,你母親會學著愛上你愛的人\N{\rENG}Your mother will learn to love who you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:25.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,彼岸花  彼岸花\N{\rENG}Tomb Bloom. Tomb Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:44.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,我要失去耐心了\N{\rENG}I'm losing my patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\rENG}Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.38,0:20:48.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,你得加快進度  馬屁精\N{\rENG}You need to move faster, Lickspittle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:50.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,遵命  陛下\N{\rENG}Yes, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:54.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,奧蘿拉答應了求婚\N{\rENG}Aurora said yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:00.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,一切即將完美\N{\rENG}It's all coming together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:04.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,上演\N{\rENG}perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:15.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rENG}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:17.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rENG}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:21.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rENG}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:25.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,試試別露太多尖牙\N{\rENG}Try it with a little less fang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:29.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,這樣如何\N{\rENG}How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:34.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,練練問好\N{\rENG}Try the greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:38.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,非常感謝你今晚的邀請\N{\rENG}How kind of you to invite me this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:40.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,記住  這不是威脅\N{\rENG}Remember, it's not a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:45.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,非常感謝你今晚的邀請\N{\rENG}So very kind of you to invite me this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:48.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,這樣好多了\N{\rENG}Yeah. Better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:50.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,加上屈膝禮試試\N{\rENG}Try it with a curtsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:54.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,不加也挺好的\N{\rENG}We can skip that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:01.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,她真的很愛那個小夥子\N{\rENG}She really loves that boy, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:04.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,你這樣做是對她的體貼\N{\rENG}You're doing her a great kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.02,0:22:08.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,體貼\N{\rENG}Kindness?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.13,0:22:10.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,夫人\N{\rENG}Mistress...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.78,0:22:25.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,她很漂亮吧\N{\rENG}Doesn't she look lovely?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:32.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,我有東西要給你\N{\rENG}I have something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.89,0:22:37.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,遮住你的角\N{\rENG}For your horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.35,0:22:39.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,我覺得這樣應該會\N{\rENG}I just thought it might make
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:41.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,讓菲力浦的家人更自在些\N{\rENG}Philip's family feel more comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.47,0:22:43.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,你也更自在些\N{\rENG}And you, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.46,0:22:48.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,也許是個餿主意\N{\rENG}Maybe it's a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.10,0:22:50.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rENG}No, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:53.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒關系\N{\rENG}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.01,0:23:04.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,我太興奮了\N{\rENG}I'm so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:07.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,我都快受不了了\N{\rENG}It's more than I can bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.13,0:23:45.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,是瑪琳菲森\N{\rENG}It's Maleficent!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.51,0:23:53.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,乾草叉\N{\rENG}Pitchforks?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.05,0:23:56.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,人類真可笑\N{\rENG}Humans are hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.15,0:24:02.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,有進步\N{\rENG}It's getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.11,0:24:20.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,擅離崗位者死\N{\rENG}Anyone leaves their post gets hung.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.42,0:24:21.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,遵命  長官\N{\rENG}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.47,0:24:32.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們到了\N{\rENG}They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.25,0:24:42.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,你考慮過把我變成熊嗎\N{\rENG}Have you ever considered turning me into a bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.65,0:24:44.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,我覺得我當熊肯定很厲害\N{\rENG}I think I'd make quite an impressive one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.05,0:24:46.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,看看這利爪  太強壯了\N{\rENG}Look at their claws. They're so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.53,0:24:48.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,你說熊幹什麼\N{\rENG}Why are we talking about bears?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.94,0:24:52.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,有請摩爾王國的奧蘿拉女王\N{\rENG}Presenting Queen Aurora of the Moors.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.42,0:25:03.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\rENG}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.76,0:25:05.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,你看起來美極了\N{\rENG}You look wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.46,0:25:07.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,能來這裡我很高興\N{\rENG}I'm so happy to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.65,0:25:12.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,奧蘿拉  見到你是莫大的榮幸\N{\rENG}Aurora, this is truly an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.42,0:25:18.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,歡迎來到奧斯戴\N{\rENG}Welcome to Ulstead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.72,0:25:22.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,真是個美麗的姑娘\N{\rENG}Such a beautiful girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.07,0:25:26.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,我明白你是怎麼偷走菲力浦的心了\N{\rENG}I can see how you stole Philip's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.43,0:25:28.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\rENG}Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.29,0:25:33.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,你頭發上的花朵\N{\rENG}The flowers in your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.53,0:25:35.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,我過敏\N{\rENG}I'm allergic.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.60,0:25:36.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\rENG}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.68,0:25:39.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,不不不  沒關系\N{\rENG}Oh, no. No, no. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.16,0:25:39.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,花朵很美\N{\rENG}They're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.97,0:25:42.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,有請瑪琳菲森\N{\rENG}Presenting Maleficent.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.12,0:25:56.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑪琳菲森  很高興再次見到你\N{\rENG}Maleficent, it's wonderful to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.92,0:26:00.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是我父親  奧斯戴王國的約翰國王\N{\rENG}This is my father, King John of Ulstead.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.51,0:26:02.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,還有我母親  英格瑞斯王后\N{\rENG}And my mother, Queen Ingrith.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.30,0:26:05.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,歡迎來我們家\N{\rENG}Welcome to our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.47,0:26:12.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,非常感謝你今晚的邀請\N{\rENG}It's so very kind of you to invite me this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.41,0:26:15.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,別笑\N{\rENG}Don't smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.41,0:26:21.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想為你們引見迪亞瓦\N{\rENG}And I would like to introduce you to Diaval.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.83,0:26:25.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,找到這座城堡應該不太麻煩吧\N{\rENG}I trust you had no trouble finding the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.72,0:26:27.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,為什麼會有麻煩\N{\rENG}Why would I have trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.08,0:26:32.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,他在和你閑聊\N{\rENG}He's making small talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.45,0:26:34.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,我晚點給你解釋\N{\rENG}I'll explain it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.03,0:26:37.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,完全沒有麻煩\N{\rENG}No trouble at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.58,0:26:39.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,國王和王后陛下  女士們先生們\N{\rENG}Your Majesties, ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.59,0:26:40.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,晚宴準備好了\N{\rENG}dinner is served.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.41,0:26:44.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,請不要拘束\N{\rENG}Please, make yourselves at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.84,0:27:14.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,鳥\N{\rENG}Bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.84,0:27:18.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,美味\N{\rENG}Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.06,0:27:28.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,有什麼問題嗎\N{\rENG}Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.93,0:27:32.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,餐具是鐵的\N{\rENG}It's iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.36,0:27:34.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,陛下  就像你對花敏感\N{\rENG}Majesty, as you are sensitive to flowers,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.68,0:27:36.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,她厭惡鐵\N{\rENG}she is averse to iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.08,0:27:39.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rENG}I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.71,0:27:41.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,立刻拿下去\N{\rENG}Take it away at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.10,0:27:50.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,你應該覺得用手更自在吧\N{\rENG}I trust you'll be comfortable using your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.61,0:27:54.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,最近天氣真暖和  不是嗎\N{\rENG}Such a warm spell of weather, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.02,0:27:56.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,確實是\N{\rENG}It certainly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.04,0:28:03.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們為菲力浦和奧蘿拉準備了一份小禮物\N{\rENG}Well, we have a small gift for Philip and Aurora...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.99,0:28:08.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,慶賀他們在一起的美好未來\N{\rENG}to celebrate their glorious future together.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.36,0:28:21.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,我等不及再次有小孩子在城堡裡跑來跑去\N{\rENG}I simply can't wait to have a little one running through the castle again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.73,0:28:26.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,這座城堡嗎\N{\rENG}This castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.11,0:28:28.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,是的  當然\N{\rENG}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.35,0:28:32.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,這裡會是他們的家\N{\rENG}This will be their home.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.28,0:28:37.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,我聽說奧蘿拉有自己的城堡\N{\rENG}I hear Aurora has a castle of her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.98,0:28:39.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,是的  陛下\N{\rENG}Yes, sir, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.03,0:28:41.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,好吧  我...\N{\rENG}Yes... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.50,0:28:43.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,我很好奇\N{\rENG}I'm curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.44,0:28:46.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,奧蘿拉是怎麼成為摩爾王國女王的\N{\rENG}How did Aurora become Queen of the Moors?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.19,0:28:48.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,我讓她當的\N{\rENG}I made her queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.52,0:28:50.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,她的城堡相當漂亮  你一定得去看看\N{\rENG}Her castle is quite stunning. You must see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.60,0:28:52.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,好吧  但事實上  她有另一座城堡\N{\rENG}Yes, but in fact, she has another castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.20,0:28:56.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,不是嗎\N{\rENG}Does she not?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.90,0:28:58.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,母親\N{\rENG}Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.44,0:28:59.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,一個在摩爾王國\N{\rENG}One in the Moors,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.35,0:29:02.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,一個她父王留下的\N{\rENG}and one left behind by her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.80,0:29:06.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,斯特凡國王的城堡  不是嗎\N{\rENG}King Stefan, was it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.48,0:29:09.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,那座城堡從不是我家  已經送給人民了\N{\rENG}That castle was never my home. It was given to the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.78,0:29:13.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,所以說你也是真正的公主\N{\rENG}So, you're also a true princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.46,0:29:15.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,雖然斯特凡死了  被殺了\N{\rENG}Even though Stefan died. Was killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.64,0:29:18.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,提醒我一下  他是死了還是被殺了\N{\rENG}Remind me, did he die or was he killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.60,0:29:19.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,被殺而死\N{\rENG}Both.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.16,0:29:24.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,你說得沒錯  最近是很暖和\N{\rENG}Yes, you're right, it is very warm recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.74,0:29:28.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,因為我記得一個嬰兒的故事\N{\rENG}Because I remember the story of a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.80,0:29:31.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,嬰兒被施咒沉睡\N{\rENG}A baby cursed to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.18,0:29:34.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,再也沒有醒來\N{\rENG}and never wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.36,0:29:36.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,真的嗎\N{\rENG}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.66,0:29:40.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,誰會對無辜的孩子做這麼可怕的事\N{\rENG}Who would do such a terrible thing to an innocent child?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.71,0:29:46.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,有很多會對無辜者下手的人\N{\rENG}Well, there are many who prey on the innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.14,0:29:49.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們一族肯定會認同\N{\rENG}I'm sure your kind would agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.77,0:29:51.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們一族是什麼意思\N{\rENG}What do you mean, my kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.36,0:29:53.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,她的意思是人類\N{\rENG}She means humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.83,0:29:55.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,摩爾王國有仙子失蹤\N{\rENG}There are fairies missing from the Moors.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.87,0:29:57.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,我缺失的是酒\N{\rENG}What I'm missing is some wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.31,0:29:59.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,被人類偷獵者偷走\N{\rENG}Stolen by human poachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.27,0:30:00.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是我第一次聽說\N{\rENG}That's the first I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.52,0:30:02.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,有人下了令\N{\rENG}Someone gave the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.54,0:30:12.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,聽起來你在指控國王\N{\rENG}It sounds as if you're accusing the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.08,0:30:14.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,不  她沒那麼說\N{\rENG}No, she never said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.45,0:30:16.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,等等  不好意思  誰會偷仙子\N{\rENG}Wait... Sorry, who would steal a fairy?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.98,0:30:18.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,陛下  我必須上報\N{\rENG}Your Majesty, I must report
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.42,0:30:21.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,兩個平民被發現死在摩爾王國外\N{\rENG}that two peasants were found dead... just outside the Moors.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.84,0:30:23.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們失蹤了好幾天\N{\rENG}They'd been missing for several days.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.75,0:30:24.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,明白了\N{\rENG}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.61,0:30:26.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們都明白了\N{\rENG}Yes, we all see.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.09,0:30:31.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,邊境開放  但並不歡迎人類  不是嗎\N{\rENG}The borders are open, but humans are not welcome. Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.15,0:30:34.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,你到底在暗示什麼  陛下\N{\rENG}What exactly are you implying, Your Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.94,0:30:37.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,無辜人類在摩爾王國被殘忍殺害\N{\rENG}Innocent men are being slaughtered on the Moors...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.84,0:30:40.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,她卻在說仙子\N{\rENG}and she's talking about fairies.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.47,0:30:46.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,管好你的動物\N{\rENG}Contain your animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.65,0:30:48.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,否則我替你管\N{\rENG}Or I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.30,0:30:54.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,要不是我明事理\N{\rENG}If I didn't know better,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.38,0:30:56.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,我會以為你在威脅\N{\rENG}I'd say you were making a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.04,0:30:57.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,你是嗎\N{\rENG}Well, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.18,0:30:59.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,-我是什麼  -明事理\N{\rENG}- Do I what? - Know better?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.28,0:31:00.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,夠了\N{\rENG}Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.45,0:31:01.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,把它放下\N{\rENG}Put her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.26,0:31:04.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,拜託  把它放下\N{\rENG}Please, put her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.11,0:31:10.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們是來慶祝的\N{\rENG}We're here to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.26,0:31:15.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,原諒我  他說得對\N{\rENG}Forgive me, he's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.61,0:31:17.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,不要忘了我們在此的原因\N{\rENG}Let's not forget why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.66,0:31:21.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,奧蘿拉新人生的開始\N{\rENG}The start of a new life for Aurora.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.80,0:31:24.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,-乾杯  -乾杯\N{\rENG}- Cheers. - Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.29,0:31:31.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑪琳菲森  你的付出令人欽佩\N{\rENG}You have done an admirable job, Maleficent...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.14,0:31:35.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,違背自己的天性撫養這個孩子\N{\rENG}going against your own nature to raise this child.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.92,0:31:37.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,但是現在\N{\rENG}But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.75,0:31:41.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,奧蘿拉終於要得到...\N{\rENG}Aurora will finally get...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.95,0:31:44.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,真正家庭的愛了\N{\rENG}the love of a real family.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.14,0:31:46.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,一位真正的母親\N{\rENG}A real mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.11,0:31:49.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,因為我唯一後悔的\N{\rENG}Because the one thing I regret...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.88,0:31:52.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,就是沒有自己的女兒\N{\rENG}is never having a daughter of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.35,0:31:55.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,但今晚改變了這點\N{\rENG}But tonight changes that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.38,0:32:01.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,今晚  我把奧蘿拉當親生女兒\N{\rENG}Tonight, I consider Aurora my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.14,0:32:17.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,衛兵\N{\rENG}Guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.12,0:32:19.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們把女巫請進了家門\N{\rENG}We have opened our home to a witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.13,0:32:31.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\rENG}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.85,0:32:33.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,不會有結盟\N{\rENG}There is no union.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.69,0:32:35.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,也不會有婚禮\N{\rENG}There will be no wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.05,0:32:37.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,-瑪琳菲森  -我們必須保護國王\N{\rENG}- Maleficent! - We must protect the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.78,0:32:39.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑪琳菲森  請你快停手\N{\rENG}Maleficent, please, stop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.82,0:32:42.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,約翰  我好害怕\N{\rENG}John, I'm so frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.79,0:32:45.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,她對我做了什麼\N{\rENG}What has she done to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.53,0:32:48.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,父親\N{\rENG}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.23,0:32:51.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,約翰\N{\rENG}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.06,0:32:53.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們回家\N{\rENG}We go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.00,0:32:55.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,約翰\N{\rENG}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.55,0:32:58.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是詛咒\N{\rENG}It's a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.99,0:33:02.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是詛咒\N{\rENG}It's a curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.69,0:33:05.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑪琳菲森對國王施咒了\N{\rENG}Maleficent has cursed the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.46,0:33:08.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,你做了什麼\N{\rENG}What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.55,0:33:09.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,我什麼都沒做\N{\rENG}I've done nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.35,0:33:13.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,奧蘿拉  我們立刻回家\N{\rENG}Aurora, we go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.90,0:33:16.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,奧蘿拉\N{\rENG}Aurora!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.65,0:33:31.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,奧蘿拉\N{\rENG}Aurora!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.06,0:33:33.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,解除詛咒\N{\rENG}Wake him!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.73,0:33:37.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,解除詛咒  求你了\N{\rENG}Wake him, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.86,0:35:01.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,都讓開\N{\rENG}Stand aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.53,0:35:05.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,快抬到臥室\N{\rENG}To the bedroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.52,0:35:10.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,這種魔力  我們沒有辦法解除\N{\rENG}This magic, we have no tools to reverse it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.86,0:35:14.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,一定有傷口\N{\rENG}There must be a lesion.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.03,0:35:16.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,她施法的證據\N{\rENG}Proof of her witchery.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.35,0:35:18.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,請為陛下保留些顏面吧\N{\rENG}Please, leave His Majesty his dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.20,0:35:22.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們都看見瑪琳菲森對他做了什麼\N{\rENG}We all saw what Maleficent did to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.58,0:35:24.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\rENG}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.11,0:35:28.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,詛咒我們的國王就是詛咒這個王國\N{\rENG}A curse upon our king is a curse upon this kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.30,0:35:31.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,他只是想要和平\N{\rENG}All he wanted was peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.29,0:35:33.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,這都是我的錯\N{\rENG}This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.43,0:35:37.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,你完全不需要道歉  親愛的\N{\rENG}You have nothing to apologize for, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.13,0:35:41.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑪琳菲森對所有人都是威脅\N{\rENG}Maleficent is a threat to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.89,0:35:43.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,對你尤其如此\N{\rENG}Especially you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.89,0:35:46.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們會盡全力保護你的\N{\rENG}We'll do our best to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.12,0:35:49.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,一定有辦法能解除詛咒\N{\rENG}There must be a way to reverse this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.98,0:35:54.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,母親  你吻他一下試試\N{\rENG}Mother, could you try kissing him?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.53,0:35:58.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,真愛之類的\N{\rENG}True love and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.88,0:36:04.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,我猜是沒用的\N{\rENG}I doubt that would work.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.80,0:36:05.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,也許能救他呢\N{\rENG}It could save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.77,0:36:08.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,-吻就只是吻  -拜託了  母親\N{\rENG}- A kiss is just a kiss. - Please, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.96,0:36:09.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rENG}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.27,0:36:22.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,你渴望和平\N{\rENG}You wanted peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.67,0:36:26.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,那就永遠和平地安息吧\N{\rENG}now rest in peace forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.68,0:36:36.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,我早說過了\N{\rENG}I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.81,0:36:40.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,這可不是童話\N{\rENG}This is no fairy tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.26,0:36:42.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,我必須回摩爾一趟\N{\rENG}I have to return to the Moors.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.70,0:36:44.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是唯一的辦法\N{\rENG}It's the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.38,0:36:46.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,等一下  過來\N{\rENG}Wait, wait. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.11,0:36:47.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,我必須找到她\N{\rENG}I have to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.38,0:36:48.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,現在已經半夜了\N{\rENG}It's the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.60,0:36:50.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,她會解開詛咒的  我知道她會的\N{\rENG}She will break the curse. I know she will.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.61,0:36:51.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,好  那讓我跟你一起去吧\N{\rENG}Okay, well, let me come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.79,0:36:55.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,不  你應該和你的家人在一起\N{\rENG}No. You should stay with your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.30,0:36:56.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,你就是我的家人\N{\rENG}You are my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.57,0:36:59.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,讓她去吧  菲力浦\N{\rENG}Let her go, Philip.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.70,0:37:02.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,也許她可以拯救國王\N{\rENG}Maybe she can save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.83,0:38:00.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑪琳菲森\N{\rENG}Maleficent!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.20,0:38:06.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑪琳菲森\N{\rENG}Maleficent!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.29,0:38:14.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,教母\N{\rENG}Godmother!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.87,0:38:23.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,求你回來\N{\rENG}Please come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.56,0:38:29.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,她不在摩爾境內\N{\rENG}She's not in the Moors.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.25,0:38:32.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,迪瓦爾\N{\rENG}Diaval.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.47,0:38:34.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒有人看到過她\N{\rENG}No one's seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.56,0:38:37.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,見到你我太高興了\N{\rENG}I'm so happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.60,0:38:40.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,哪裡都找不到她\N{\rENG}She's nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.90,0:38:43.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果她再也不回來怎麼辦\N{\rENG}What if she never comes back?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.61,0:38:45.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,那我就要永遠保持人形了\N{\rENG}I could be stuck as a human forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.13,0:38:47.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,我必須找到她\N{\rENG}I have to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.53,0:38:52.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,只有她能解開詛咒\N{\rENG}She's the only one who can break the curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.39,0:39:55.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,告訴我  她已經死了\N{\rENG}Tell me she's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.82,0:39:57.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,鐵珠擊穿了她的身體\N{\rENG}The iron pierced her flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.42,0:40:01.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,她掉進河裡  墜下了瀑布\N{\rENG}She fell into the river and went over the falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.31,0:40:04.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,那她的頭顱在哪裡\N{\rENG}Then where is her head?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.57,0:40:07.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,出現了別的東西\N{\rENG}There was something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.89,0:40:09.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,另一個怪物\N{\rENG}Another creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.31,0:40:12.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,它把她從海底救了起來\N{\rENG}It pulled her from the depths of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.61,0:40:15.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,它長什麼樣\N{\rENG}What did it look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.00,0:40:16.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,和她一樣\N{\rENG}Her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.66,0:40:20.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,它抱著她飛上了天空\N{\rENG}It carried her up into the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.04,0:40:22.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,受傷的野獸突然發狂\N{\rENG}A wounded animal lashes out
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.89,0:40:24.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,而現在她有同夥了\N{\rENG}and now she's not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.61,0:40:26.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們必須做好開戰的準備\N{\rENG}We must be ready for war.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.24,0:40:32.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑪琳菲森對國王施咒了\N{\rENG}Maleficent has cursed the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.08,0:40:39.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,待在室內\N{\rENG}Stay inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.19,0:40:49.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑪琳菲森對國王施咒了\N{\rENG}Maleficent has cursed the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.90,0:42:25.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,要不是康諾爾找到她  她早沒命了\N{\rENG}If Conall hadn't found her, she would be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.55,0:42:31.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們想用這玩意兒殺死她\N{\rENG}They tried to kill her with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.07,0:42:49.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們聽到了嗎\N{\rENG}Do you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.58,0:42:52.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們聽到了嗎\N{\rENG}Do you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.21,0:42:58.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是人類發出的信號\N{\rENG}It's a message from the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.40,0:43:01.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,我聽得再清楚不過了\N{\rENG}I hear it loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.81,0:43:03.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們生死存亡的時刻到了\N{\rENG}Time for us to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.30,0:43:08.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,幾百年來  人類一直用鐵來對付我們\N{\rENG}Humans have used iron against us for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.93,0:43:11.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們差點因此滅族\N{\rENG}And we are almost extinct because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.45,0:43:12.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,屠殺摩爾的平民\N{\rENG}Killing peasants on the Moors
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.91,0:43:15.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,只會引發更多的沖突  博拉\N{\rENG}will only lead to more conflict, Borra.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.80,0:43:17.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,人類從土地中挖出鐵\N{\rENG}They've pulled the iron from the earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.68,0:43:20.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,做成劍和盾  把我們逼到了地底\N{\rENG}made their swords and shields, drove us underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.37,0:43:21.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,而這個\N{\rENG}But this...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.22,0:43:26.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,會讓我們徹底滅亡\N{\rENG}This will finish us.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.29,0:43:28.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們在這裡仍然安全\N{\rENG}Our people are safe here for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.17,0:43:29.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,但能維持多久呢\N{\rENG}But for how long?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.46,0:43:32.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,人類會找到我們  他們不會停手\N{\rENG}The humans will find us. They will not stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.66,0:43:33.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,我提議發動戰爭\N{\rENG}I call for war.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.27,0:43:37.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,我提議發動戰爭\N{\rENG}I call for war!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.14,0:43:39.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,刻不容緩\N{\rENG}Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.46,0:43:42.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,人類的數量太多了\N{\rENG}There are too many humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.96,0:43:46.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,人類的王國太多了\N{\rENG}Too many kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.16,0:43:48.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,康諾爾  人類會不停地尋找\N{\rENG}Conall, they will keep finding
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.30,0:43:50.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,毀滅我們的新手段\N{\rENG}new ways to destroy us.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.27,0:43:51.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們贏不了\N{\rENG}We can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.00,0:43:57.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們贏不了\N{\rENG}We can't win!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.99,0:44:02.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,靠戰爭贏不了\N{\rENG}Not this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.35,0:44:05.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,不  你錯了  康諾爾\N{\rENG}No. You're wrong, Conall.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.92,0:44:08.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們有他們意想不到的絕招\N{\rENG}We have something they didn't plan on.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.31,0:44:13.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們有她\N{\rENG}We have her.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.20,0:44:21.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,她有我們任何人都不具備的力量\N{\rENG}She holds powers none of us possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.41,0:44:24.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,她受傷了  博拉\N{\rENG}She is wounded, Borra.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.08,0:44:27.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們是誰\N{\rENG}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.04,0:44:45.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,你散發著人類的惡臭\N{\rENG}You reek of human.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.20,0:44:49.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,也許我看錯了你\N{\rENG}Maybe I was wrong about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.49,0:44:52.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,也許康諾爾應該把你留在海底\N{\rENG}Or maybe Conall should have left you for dead
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.23,0:44:53.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,任由你死去\N{\rENG}at the bottom of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.77,0:44:58.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,不對\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.52,0:45:01.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,它確實存在  對嗎\N{\rENG}It's there, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.06,0:45:05.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,它就在你體內\N{\rENG}It's inside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.58,0:45:25.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們看到了嗎\N{\rENG}You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.61,0:45:31.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們看到她體內的力量了嗎\N{\rENG}You see what's inside her?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.68,0:45:35.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,那將能拯救我們所有人\N{\rENG}That is what will save us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.38,0:45:54.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,你救了我\N{\rENG}You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.64,0:45:59.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,跟我來\N{\rENG}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.48,0:46:06.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,我帶你看我們是誰\N{\rENG}Let me show you who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.84,0:47:04.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們是黑暗仙子\N{\rENG}We're Dark Fey.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.65,0:47:07.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,和你一樣\N{\rENG}Same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.87,0:47:20.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們是僅存的黑暗仙子了\N{\rENG}We're all that remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.83,0:47:24.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,躲藏在此處  遠離人類\N{\rENG}Unseen here, far away from mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.81,0:47:25.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,快看\N{\rENG}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.31,0:47:29.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,當越來越多的人類王國出現\N{\rENG}As more human kingdoms emerged,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.03,0:47:30.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,世界各個角落的我們\N{\rENG}we went into hiding...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.59,0:47:32.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,不得不躲藏起來\N{\rENG}from every corner of the earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.12,0:47:35.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,為了生存竭盡全力\N{\rENG}doing what we had to, to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.37,0:47:38.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,但我們失去了很多同伴\N{\rENG}But many were lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.42,0:48:03.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,僅僅幾代仙子之前\N{\rENG}Only a few generations ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.82,0:48:06.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們一族遍佈世界各處\N{\rENG}our kind roamed every part of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.80,0:48:09.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,凍土平原\N{\rENG}The tundra.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.51,0:48:10.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,森林\N{\rENG}The forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.94,0:48:12.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,叢林\N{\rENG}The jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.10,0:48:17.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,沙漠\N{\rENG}The desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.35,0:48:25.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,如今  我們僅存的避難所\N{\rENG}Now, our only refuge is here...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.88,0:48:27.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,就是這個洞穴\N{\rENG}in this cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.99,0:48:29.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們祖先的巢穴\N{\rENG}Our nest of origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.74,0:48:37.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,聽著  去風中玩耍吧\N{\rENG}Listen. Play in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.19,0:48:40.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\rENG}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.70,0:49:03.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,那些孩子本該在樹林和河流上方遨遊\N{\rENG}Those children should be soaring over the trees and rivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.64,0:49:05.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,然而他們只能在流亡中長大\N{\rENG}Instead, they are raised in exile.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.21,0:49:07.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,我能保護他們\N{\rENG}I could protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.53,0:49:12.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,怎麼保護  靠跟人類開戰嗎\N{\rENG}How? By waging war against the humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.24,0:49:14.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,我一生都在和人類鬥爭\N{\rENG}I've been at war with them my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.31,0:49:15.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,並非所有的人類\N{\rENG}Not all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.28,0:49:18.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,有一個人類孩子你視如己出\N{\rENG}There was one you raised as your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.76,0:49:23.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,也許我們不需要躲避人類\N{\rENG}Maybe we don't have to hide from the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.26,0:49:26.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,也許我們能生存下去  擺脫恐懼\N{\rENG}Maybe we can exist without fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.52,0:49:27.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,擺脫戰爭\N{\rENG}and war.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.76,0:49:30.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,找到共存的辦法\N{\rENG}Find a way together.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.63,0:49:34.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,那永遠不可能實現\N{\rENG}That will never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.72,0:51:08.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,抓到你啦\N{\rENG}Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.20,0:51:15.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,歡迎來到你的新家\N{\rENG}Welcome to your new home.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.75,0:51:36.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們都很擔心你  親愛的\N{\rENG}We've been worried about you, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.33,0:51:39.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\rENG}Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.51,0:51:41.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,我找不到她\N{\rENG}I couldn't find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.90,0:51:44.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,我真為你心碎\N{\rENG}My heart breaks for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.95,0:51:49.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,她為你的幸福蒙上了一層烏雲\N{\rENG}She has brought a cloud of darkness upon your happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.44,0:51:52.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道她反對這門婚事\N{\rENG}I know she was against this marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.36,0:51:56.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,她也未曾信任過你作為女王的直覺\N{\rENG}Never trusted your instincts as a queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.67,0:51:58.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,當我在晚宴上見到她\N{\rENG}When I saw her at dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.58,0:52:04.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,她的角被遮蓋住\N{\rENG}with her horns covered...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.83,0:52:08.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,掩飾著扭曲\N{\rENG}bent cowering...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.51,0:52:10.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rENG}Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.62,0:52:15.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,她突然發狂一點也不奇怪\N{\rENG}it's no wonder that she lashed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.12,0:52:19.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不知道該怎麼做\N{\rENG}I just don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.33,0:52:21.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,你確實很愛他  不是嗎\N{\rENG}You do truly love him, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.90,0:52:23.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的兒子\N{\rENG}My son.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.89,0:52:25.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,我深愛著他\N{\rENG}Deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.18,0:52:29.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,愛會治癒你\N{\rENG}It is love that will heal you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.72,0:52:31.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,愛會治癒我們所有人\N{\rENG}It's what heals us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.08,0:52:34.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,讓我們作為一家人\N{\rENG}Let's move forward together...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.13,0:52:37.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,一起向前看\N{\rENG}as a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.41,0:52:56.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,致摩爾王國的所有生靈\N{\rENG}To all who live on the Moors...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.28,0:53:01.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,那是什麼聲音\N{\rENG}What is that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.50,0:53:03.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,以及遠方的各國\N{\rENG}...and kingdoms far and wide,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.02,0:53:04.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們的國王和王后邀請你們\N{\rENG}the king and queen invite you...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.56,0:53:06.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,來參加他們的兒子菲力浦\N{\rENG}to attend the wedding...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.72,0:53:10.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,和奧蘿拉在三天后的婚禮\N{\rENG}of their son Philip to Aurora in three days' time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.04,0:53:12.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,歡迎所有生靈\N{\rENG}All are welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.52,0:53:17.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,所有生靈都應該到場\N{\rENG}And all are expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.41,0:53:22.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,你聽到了嗎  我們被邀請去城堡了\N{\rENG}Did you hear that? We're invited to the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.08,0:53:24.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,我就知道奧蘿拉不會丟下我們\N{\rENG}I knew Aurora wouldn't abandon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.10,0:53:26.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,我一直都知道自己會受邀的\N{\rENG}I always knew I'd be invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.49,0:53:28.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,很高興你倆也能參加\N{\rENG}Just glad you two made the cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.41,0:53:30.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,誰要結婚了\N{\rENG}Who's getting married?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.59,0:53:42.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,奧蘿拉  我們不用著急婚禮的事\N{\rENG}Aurora, we don't have to think about the wedding right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.94,0:53:46.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,王后說得對\N{\rENG}The queen is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.84,0:53:48.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們需要對大家有交代\N{\rENG}We owe it to everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.66,0:53:51.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,尤其是國王\N{\rENG}especially the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.71,0:53:54.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,那瑪琳菲森呢\N{\rENG}What about Maleficent?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.87,0:53:59.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,她已經不在了\N{\rENG}She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.87,0:54:14.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,鳳凰\N{\rENG}The Phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.38,0:54:17.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,傳說她是黑暗仙子的祖先\N{\rENG}It is said the Dark Fey began with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.93,0:54:19.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,經過了幾個世紀的演化\N{\rENG}evolved over centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.76,0:54:24.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,你是她最後的後裔\N{\rENG}You are the last of her descendants.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.83,0:54:26.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,你和她血脈相連\N{\rENG}Her blood is your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.84,0:54:30.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,你就是她\N{\rENG}You are her.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.90,0:54:36.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,你手中掌握著控制生死的能力\N{\rENG}In your hands, you hold the power of life and death...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.38,0:54:39.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,毀滅和重生\N{\rENG}destruction and rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.72,0:54:43.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,但自然最大的力量\N{\rENG}But nature's greatest power
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.07,0:54:47.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,是真正蛻變的力量\N{\rENG}is the power of true transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.18,0:54:52.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,你在撫養奧蘿拉時蛻變了\N{\rENG}You transformed when you raised Aurora.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.34,0:54:56.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,你在痛苦中\N{\rENG}When you found love...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.58,0:54:59.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,找到了愛\N{\rENG}in the middle of your pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.62,0:55:04.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,我請求你把你的一切憤怒\N{\rENG}I'm asking you to take all of your fury...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.96,0:55:06.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,一切痛苦\N{\rENG}all of your pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.01,0:55:09.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,全部摒棄\N{\rENG}and not use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.68,0:55:12.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,幫助我們與人類和平共處\N{\rENG}Help us broker peace with the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.93,0:55:15.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,因為和平\N{\rENG}Because peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.65,0:55:21.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,可能會是黑暗仙子最後的蛻變\N{\rENG}could be the Dark Fey's final transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.63,0:55:31.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,摩爾王國是我們在世上最後的凈土\N{\rENG}The Moors are our last true nature on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.98,0:55:35.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,而你讓一個人類當了女王\N{\rENG}And yet you named a human as queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.98,0:55:39.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,你愛護的女兒\N{\rENG}A daughter you cared for.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.65,0:55:43.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,我沒有女兒\N{\rENG}I have no daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.64,0:55:48.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,她已經選擇了自己的立場\N{\rENG}She has chosen her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.35,0:56:02.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們剛剛聽說\N{\rENG}We've just heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.46,0:56:06.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,三天后城堡中會舉行婚禮\N{\rENG}There's going to be a wedding at the castle in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.66,0:56:09.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,各地的人類都會過去\N{\rENG}Humans will come from all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.49,0:56:12.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們就在那時進攻\N{\rENG}That's when we attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.46,0:56:14.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,殺了奧斯戴的國王和王后\N{\rENG}We'll kill the king and queen of Ulstead...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.54,0:56:17.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,還有他們的小王子\N{\rENG}and their young prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.55,0:56:21.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們的王國將會滅亡\N{\rENG}Their kingdom will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.74,0:56:24.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,仙子將再次崛起\N{\rENG}And the Fey will rise again.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.69,0:56:42.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是仙子們做的\N{\rENG}The fairies made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.79,0:57:01.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是我嫁給國王時穿的\N{\rENG}I wore it when I married the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.14,0:57:11.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,肯定是完美的嫁衣\N{\rENG}I'm sure it's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.83,0:57:14.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,我同意\N{\rENG}So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.20,0:57:23.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,陛下  她真漂亮\N{\rENG}Your Majesty, she's absolutely lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.10,0:57:24.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,考慮到她的身世背景\N{\rENG}Considering how she was raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.79,0:57:26.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,被那個對她施咒的邪惡女巫撫養長大\N{\rENG}By the same evil witch who cursed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.90,0:57:30.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,她能遇上菲力浦王子真是奇跡\N{\rENG}It's a miracle Prince Philip came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.36,0:57:32.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,這可憐的姑娘能活下來就是奇跡了\N{\rENG}It's a miracle the poor child is alive at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.67,0:57:36.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,非常感謝\N{\rENG}Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.97,0:57:38.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,太精美了\N{\rENG}It's exquisite.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.43,0:58:09.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,等我長大了\N{\rENG}When I'm older...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.75,0:58:12.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,就和你一起住在摩爾王國\N{\rENG}I'm going to live here, in the Moors, with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.09,0:58:15.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,這樣我們就能相互照顧\N{\rENG}Then we can look after each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.46,0:58:39.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,-跟我說說你有什麼煩心事  -沒什麼\N{\rENG}- Tell me what's troubling you. - It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.95,0:58:42.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,奧蘿拉  我瞭解你\N{\rENG}Aurora, I know you better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.32,0:58:47.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,這些珠寶\N{\rENG}This jewelry...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.58,0:58:48.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的發型\N{\rENG}my hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.86,0:58:50.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,那麼多規矩\N{\rENG}all these rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.78,0:58:53.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,讓我喘不過氣\N{\rENG}I just... I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.93,0:58:57.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,我感覺自己不再是摩爾王國的女王了\N{\rENG}I feel like I'm not Queen of the Moors anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.81,0:58:59.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,我感覺像變了個人\N{\rENG}I feel like a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.44,0:59:01.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,聽著\N{\rENG}Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.05,0:59:05.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,我愛上的是森林裡的那個女孩  並且只愛她\N{\rENG}I fell in love with a girl in the forest and only her.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.57,0:59:07.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不必改變\N{\rENG}You don't have to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.02,0:59:08.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不想讓你改變\N{\rENG}I don't want you to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.64,0:59:20.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,我真不該讓她戴頭巾\N{\rENG}I should have never asked her to wear that scarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.14,0:59:28.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\shad1}鐵粉
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.91,0:59:42.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\rENG}Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.40,0:59:44.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣\N{\rENG}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.74,0:59:47.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,成功了嗎\N{\rENG}Does it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.35,0:59:50.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,我只有屈指可數的幾個仙子用來試驗\N{\rENG}I only have a handful of fairy specimens to work with...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.61,0:59:53.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,而且提取過程很艱難\N{\rENG}and the extraction process is painstaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.83,0:59:56.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,提取什麼\N{\rENG}Extraction from what?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.45,0:59:57.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,彼岸花\N{\rENG}Tomb Bloom flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.93,0:59:59.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,它們生長于仙子的墳墓\N{\rENG}They grow from a fairy's grave,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.77,1:00:01.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,含有仙子的精華\N{\rENG}contain their very essence.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.83,1:00:03.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,將它的花粉與鐵粉混合\N{\rENG}When you mix the pollen with iron powder...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.86,1:00:06.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,形成的粉末能殺死仙子\N{\rENG}the resulting dust ends a fairy's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.75,1:00:08.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們需要幾千朵彼岸花\N{\rENG}We will need thousands more.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.16,1:00:11.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,演示一下\N{\rENG}Show me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.61,1:00:15.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,演示一下\N{\rENG}Show me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.47,1:00:16.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rENG}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.62,1:00:20.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,來吧\N{\rENG}So...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.51,1:01:14.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,摩爾王國終於是我的囊中之物了\N{\rENG}Finally, the Moors will be mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.70,1:01:18.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,仙子將不復存在\N{\rENG}No more fairies.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.44,1:01:53.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,保持警惕  兄弟們\N{\rENG}Stay alert, men.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.96,1:02:13.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,就是在這裡找到的\N{\rENG}This is where I found them.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.24,1:02:14.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rENG}Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.31,1:02:16.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,萬一長翅膀的怪物回來怎麼辦\N{\rENG}But what if the winged one returns?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.57,1:02:18.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,用不著擔心\N{\rENG}Don't you worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.78,1:02:20.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們會做好準備\N{\rENG}We'll be ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.80,1:02:22.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,去摘彼岸花吧\N{\rENG}Take the Tomb Blooms.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.52,1:02:24.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,動手吧\N{\rENG}Get to work!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.33,1:02:41.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,哨兵  保持警惕\N{\rENG}Sentries, stay alert!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.49,1:02:43.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,準備好武器\N{\rENG}Keep your weapons on hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.20,1:03:04.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,麻利點\N{\rENG}Move it!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.52,1:03:13.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑪琳菲森\N{\rENG}Maleficent...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.19,1:03:59.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們在這裡安葬死者\N{\rENG}This is where we bury our dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.43,1:04:03.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,被他們摧毀了\N{\rENG}They've destroyed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.86,1:04:09.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,人類就是這樣\N{\rENG}This is what the humans do.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.32,1:04:12.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們不過是擠滿大地的蝗蟲\N{\rENG}They're nothing but locusts that swarm the earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.78,1:04:14.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們必須阻止他們\N{\rENG}We have to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.02,1:04:19.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,你花了很多年照顧一個人類\N{\rENG}You spent years caring for a human...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.41,1:04:22.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,現在該照顧你自己的同類了\N{\rENG}now it's time to care for your own.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.54,1:04:33.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,射擊\N{\rENG}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.50,1:04:56.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,填彈  再來\N{\rENG}Reload! We go again!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.32,1:05:03.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,射擊\N{\rENG}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.31,1:05:09.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,填彈  還有一個\N{\rENG}Reload! There's another one!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.65,1:06:28.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,大家跟緊點\N{\rENG}Everyone, stay together!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.68,1:06:30.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們要離開摩爾王國了\N{\rENG}We're about to leave the Moors.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.52,1:06:34.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,握住離你最近的手或翅膀  或尾巴\N{\rENG}Grab the hand or the wing... or the tail of whoever is closest to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.77,1:07:18.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,這邊  這邊\N{\rENG}Hey, over here! Yeah, over here!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.95,1:07:21.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,維持隊形  衛兵們  維持隊形\N{\rENG}Hold formation, guards. Hold formation.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.07,1:07:25.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,-不好意思  先生  -站住\N{\rENG}- Excuse me, sir. - Stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.24,1:07:26.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,我是新娘那邊的\N{\rENG}I'm with the bride.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.10,1:07:29.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們奉命讓怪物先就座\N{\rENG}We've been told to let the, uh, other kind find their seats first.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.41,1:07:30.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,但我不是人類\N{\rENG}But I'm not a human.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.77,1:07:32.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,-我是烏鴉  -什麼\N{\rENG}- I'm a raven. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.64,1:07:35.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,我是烏鴉  黑色的鳥\N{\rENG}A raven. The black bird.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.20,1:07:38.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,這米真好吃\N{\rENG}This rice is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.05,1:07:40.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是用來撒向新娘和新郎的\N{\rENG}You're supposed to throw it at the bride and groom.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.49,1:07:43.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,什麼  浪費好好的米\N{\rENG}What? And waste good rice?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.32,1:07:44.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,為什麼要攔著我們\N{\rENG}What's the hold up?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.39,1:07:46.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,讓我進去\N{\rENG}Let me in!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.45,1:07:49.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,為什麼人類不能進去\N{\rENG}Why can't humans come in, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.19,1:07:51.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,為什麼我們不能進去\N{\rENG}Why can't we come in?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.12,1:08:00.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道這樣不吉利\N{\rENG}I know it's bad luck...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.13,1:08:01.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,但我必須見你\N{\rENG}but I had to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.56,1:08:04.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,給你的\N{\rENG}For you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.65,1:08:06.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,彼岸花\N{\rENG}A Tomb Bloom?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.89,1:08:07.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,你從哪里弄來的\N{\rENG}Where did you get this?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.78,1:08:09.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,從我母親那裡拿的\N{\rENG}From my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.56,1:08:12.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,天亮了  今天是我們的大喜之日\N{\rENG}The sun's up. It's our wedding day.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.08,1:08:21.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,從我母親那裡拿的\N{\rENG}From my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.29,1:11:12.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們該坐在哪裡  藍蝶仙子\N{\rENG}Where should we sit, Flittle?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.08,1:11:15.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,坐在左邊  我們是新娘那邊的\N{\rENG}On the left. We're with the bride.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.21,1:11:16.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\rENG}Yes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.84,1:11:18.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,但新郎也很可愛\N{\rENG}But the groom's lovely, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.76,1:11:20.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\rENG}Yes, he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.30,1:11:22.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,我兩邊都是\N{\rENG}I'm with both.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.10,1:11:33.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rENG}Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.00,1:11:57.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事\N{\rENG}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.67,1:12:00.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,除了我  誰都不許進來\N{\rENG}Nobody is allowed in here except me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.92,1:12:03.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,而我已經進來了  所以趕緊出去\N{\rENG}And I'm already here, so go away!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.86,1:12:24.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑪琳菲森  請你快停手\N{\rENG}Maleficent, please stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.33,1:12:31.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑪琳菲森\N{\rENG}Maleficent.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.66,1:12:33.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,不是她做的\N{\rENG}She didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.58,1:12:38.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,出去\N{\rENG}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.67,1:12:41.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,否則我叫衛兵來了\N{\rENG}Before I call the guards!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.93,1:12:49.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,失蹤的仙子\N{\rENG}The missing fairies.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.47,1:12:51.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,我說了出去  你聽到了嗎\N{\rENG}I said get out. Did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.56,1:12:52.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,你做了什麼\N{\rENG}What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.23,1:12:59.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,你是精靈\N{\rENG}You're a pixie.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.69,1:13:01.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,你竟敢這麼叫我\N{\rENG}How dare you call me that?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.73,1:13:03.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,我是貴族馬屁精\N{\rENG}I'm Lickspittle, the nobleman...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.57,1:13:05.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,我是王后的手下\N{\rENG}and I serve the queen.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.32,1:13:08.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,她奪走了你的翅膀\N{\rENG}She took your wings.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.08,1:13:13.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們得放了他們\N{\rENG}We have to release them.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.12,1:13:15.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們屬于摩爾王國\N{\rENG}They belong on the Moors.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.58,1:13:17.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,你也是  奧蘿拉\N{\rENG}As you do, Aurora.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.92,1:13:22.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,一個背叛了同類的人類\N{\rENG}A human who has betrayed her kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.09,1:13:31.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,是你對國王施了咒\N{\rENG}You put the curse on the king.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.30,1:13:32.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,親愛的\N{\rENG}Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.22,1:13:34.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,你或許是女王\N{\rENG}You may be queen...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.68,1:13:37.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,但你太年輕了\N{\rENG}but you are very young.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.52,1:13:40.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,統治人類比你頭戴鮮花\N{\rENG}Ruling humans is a bit more complicated...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.65,1:13:44.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,赤腳到處跑要更復雜\N{\rENG}than running around barefoot with flowers in your hair.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.40,1:13:48.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,我年輕時\N{\rENG}When I was young...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.91,1:13:53.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,我娘家的王國與摩爾王國接壤\N{\rENG}my family's kingdom bordered the Moors.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.49,1:13:58.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,在一個異常寒冷的冬天\N{\rENG}And one particularly harsh winter...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.00,1:13:59.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們的莊稼死了\N{\rENG}our crops died...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.75,1:14:02.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,人民開始遭罪\N{\rENG}and the people began to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.55,1:14:05.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們的視線越過城墻\N{\rENG}And as we looked over our walls...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.88,1:14:09.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,看到仙子繁榮生活著\N{\rENG}we could see the fairies thriving.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.39,1:14:13.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,我哥哥和我認為應該奪取所需\N{\rENG}My brother and I believed we should take what we needed...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.14,1:14:17.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,但我的父王親卻指望著仙子的仁慈\N{\rENG}while my father, the king, sought their kindness.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.19,1:14:21.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,選擇了和平  而不是我們的子民\N{\rENG}Choosing peace over our people,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.27,1:14:23.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,他派我哥哥去商議\N{\rENG}he sent my brother to do his bidding.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.82,1:14:25.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,但他一去不回\N{\rENG}He never came back.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.36,1:14:28.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,那些野蠻的\N{\rENG}Those savages...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.07,1:14:30.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,連話都不會說的怪物\N{\rENG}creatures who could barely grunt,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.57,1:14:32.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,不由分說地殺了他\N{\rENG}let alone engage in talks, killed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.87,1:14:35.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不相信\N{\rENG}I don't believe that.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.41,1:14:37.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們的人民開始恐懼\N{\rENG}Our people became fearful.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.04,1:14:39.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們推翻了我父王\N{\rENG}They overthrew my father.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.83,1:14:43.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,王國陷入混亂  我被驅逐了\N{\rENG}The land fell into chaos. I was cast out.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.25,1:14:48.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,命運迫使我嫁給了奧斯戴的約翰國王\N{\rENG}Forced by fate into marriage with King John of Ulstead.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.30,1:14:50.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,又是一個軟弱的國王\N{\rENG}Another weak king
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.22,1:14:52.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,滿口包容與禮待\N{\rENG}speaking of tolerance and civility.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.84,1:14:55.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,現在  我的親生兒子\N{\rENG}And now, my own son...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.18,1:14:57.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,也被追求和諧的幻想蒙蔽了\N{\rENG}corrupted with visions of harmony.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.60,1:15:02.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,但我們不會被和平毀滅\N{\rENG}But peace will not be our downfall.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.03,1:15:08.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,把她鎖起來\N{\rENG}Now lock her up.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.78,1:15:11.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,戰爭就要來了\N{\rENG}A war is coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.83,1:15:19.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,不  不\N{\rENG}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.96,1:15:29.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,真希望你能出席婚禮\N{\rENG}I wish you could be here with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.72,1:15:41.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,康諾爾想要和平\N{\rENG}Conall wanted peace...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.52,1:15:45.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們卻用鐵攻擊他\N{\rENG}and they filled him with iron.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.73,1:15:50.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們的戰爭要打響了\N{\rENG}Now, we will have our war.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.11,1:15:55.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們的戰鬥現在開始\N{\rENG}Our fight begins now!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.62,1:15:58.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們將一起崛起\N{\rENG}We will rise together!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.79,1:16:00.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們一起戰鬥\N{\rENG}We fight together.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.54,1:16:04.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們絕不會手下留情\N{\rENG}And we will show them no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.02,1:16:23.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,快點  出發\N{\rENG}Come on! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.52,1:16:30.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,快  快\N{\rENG}Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.23,1:16:33.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,快  快  快\N{\rENG}Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.00,1:16:49.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,菲力浦的客人都在哪\N{\rENG}Where are all Philip's guests?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.88,1:16:52.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,人類真不守時\N{\rENG}Humans are poor timekeepers.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.57,1:17:20.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,開始奏樂\N{\rENG}Start the music.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.84,1:17:41.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,快點  快點\N{\rENG}Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.91,1:18:45.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,她不見了\N{\rENG}She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.71,1:19:01.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,是陷阱  躲起來\N{\rENG}It's a trap! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.82,1:19:21.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\rENG}Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.41,1:19:24.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們從海上來了\N{\rENG}they're coming from the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.88,1:19:35.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,她逃走了\N{\rENG}She escaped!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.01,1:19:43.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,這邊走  快點\N{\rENG}Down this way, come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.81,1:19:52.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\rENG}Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.44,1:19:55.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,聽我指揮\N{\rENG}Upon my command.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.41,1:20:06.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,檢查每一間屋子\N{\rENG}Check every room!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.24,1:20:10.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,她跑不遠的\N{\rENG}She can't be far!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.07,1:20:44.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,等著\N{\rENG}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.66,1:20:46.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,等著\N{\rENG}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.30,1:21:11.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事\N{\rENG}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.56,1:21:17.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,發射\N{\rENG}Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.90,1:21:19.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,發射\N{\rENG}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.11,1:21:28.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rENG}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.23,1:21:57.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們看起來和她一樣\N{\rENG}They look just like her.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.40,1:22:04.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,撤退\N{\rENG}Withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.28,1:22:05.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,撤退\N{\rENG}Withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.24,1:22:09.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,撤退\N{\rENG}Pull back!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.03,1:22:10.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑪琳菲森挑起了戰爭\N{\rENG}Maleficent's starting a war.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.49,1:22:12.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,先是我父親  現在又這樣\N{\rENG}First my father, and now this.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.91,1:22:14.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,菲力浦  她沒有對他施咒\N{\rENG}Philip! She didn't curse him.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.20,1:22:17.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,-瑪琳菲森  -什麼\N{\rENG}- Maleficent. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.33,1:22:18.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,她根本沒有對他施咒\N{\rENG}She never cursed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.25,1:22:21.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,是你母親做的\N{\rENG}It was your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.88,1:22:23.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼\N{\rENG}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.21,1:22:24.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,是紡錘\N{\rENG}It was the spindle.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.88,1:22:31.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,上面還有詛咒\N{\rENG}The curse is still in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.64,1:22:33.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,你母親用它對付你父親\N{\rENG}Your mother used it against your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.06,1:22:36.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,看\N{\rENG}Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.19,1:22:41.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,一模一樣\N{\rENG}It's the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.73,1:22:43.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,她把摩爾居民鎖在了教堂裡\N{\rENG}She's locked the Moor folk in the chapel.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.44,1:22:45.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,這不是婚禮\N{\rENG}This isn't a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.94,1:22:46.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,而是陷阱\N{\rENG}It's a trap.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.32,1:22:54.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,記住你來自哪裡\N{\rENG}Remember where you came from.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.99,1:22:57.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,記住你是誰\N{\rENG}Remember who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.17,1:23:02.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,我已經做出了選擇\N{\rENG}I've made my choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.25,1:23:05.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,你也得做出選擇\N{\rENG}You'll have to make yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.37,1:23:35.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,飛低一點\N{\rENG}Stay low!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.29,1:23:39.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,散開\N{\rENG}Divide!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.58,1:23:43.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,跟著我\N{\rENG}Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.30,1:23:53.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,進攻\N{\rENG}Attack!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.64,1:23:56.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,進攻\N{\rENG}Attack!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.19,1:24:09.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,-點火  -點火\N{\rENG}- Ignite! - Ignite!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.58,1:24:21.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rENG}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.66,1:25:06.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,姑母  姑母\N{\rENG}Aunties! Aunties!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.08,1:25:10.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,太重了\N{\rENG}It's too heavy!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.92,1:25:12.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,奧蘿拉\N{\rENG}Aurora!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.96,1:25:14.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,迪亞瓦  你來了\N{\rENG}Diaval! You're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.09,1:25:19.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事\N{\rENG}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.28,1:25:41.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,換武器\N{\rENG}Weapon change!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.12,1:25:44.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,換武器  快\N{\rENG}Weapon change! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.79,1:26:25.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,母親\N{\rENG}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.62,1:26:27.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,你得阻止這一切\N{\rENG}You have to stop this.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.37,1:26:29.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們在打仗\N{\rENG}We are at war.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.54,1:26:31.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,這不是戰爭  這是屠殺\N{\rENG}This isn't a war. It's a massacre.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.50,1:26:33.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,菲力浦  你不明白\N{\rENG}Philip, you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.63,1:26:36.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,這些怪物阻擋我們\N{\rENG}These creatures stand between us...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.34,1:26:39.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,獲取生存所需的資源\N{\rENG}and everything we need to survive.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.22,1:26:40.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,你錯了\N{\rENG}You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.72,1:26:42.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們可以共存\N{\rENG}We can stand together.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.18,1:26:44.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,你這個傻瓜居然真信\N{\rENG}Well, you're a fool to believe that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.72,1:26:48.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不知道為我們的同類而戰要付出什麼\N{\rENG}You don't know what it takes to fight for our kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.18,1:26:50.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,你騙了我\N{\rENG}You lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.69,1:26:53.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,我是在保護王國\N{\rENG}I am protecting the kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.65,1:26:55.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,以及你的王位\N{\rENG}and your throne.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.32,1:26:57.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,那父親呢\N{\rENG}What about Father?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.15,1:27:00.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,你也是在保護他嗎\N{\rENG}Were you protecting him, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.58,1:27:06.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,王子身體不適\N{\rENG}The prince is not feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.04,1:27:09.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,帶他回房休息\N{\rENG}See him to his chambers.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.08,1:27:14.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,馬上\N{\rENG}Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.47,1:27:20.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,殿下  不要\N{\rENG}Sire, stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.49,1:27:49.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,停手  停手\N{\rENG}Yield! Yield!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.24,1:27:50.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,我母親對國王施咒\N{\rENG}My mother cursed the king
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.37,1:27:52.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,目的是毀滅摩爾居民\N{\rENG}so she could destroy the Moor folk.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.16,1:27:53.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,你的手下正在為此付出慘重代價\N{\rENG}Your men are paying heavily for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.05,1:28:02.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們必須做點什麼\N{\rENG}We have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.22,1:28:08.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,再見  姐妹們\N{\rENG}Goodbye, girls.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.77,1:28:11.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,不  回來\N{\rENG}No, come back!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.27,1:28:14.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,藍蝶仙子  不\N{\rENG}Flittle! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.41,1:28:28.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rENG}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.12,1:28:29.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,去跟同類待在一起\N{\rENG}Hey, you, stay with your own!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.20,1:28:31.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,快跑  奧蘿拉  快跑\N{\rENG}Run, Aurora, run!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.91,1:28:33.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,放開他\N{\rENG}Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.17,1:28:40.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,不  不\N{\rENG}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.53,1:29:08.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,教母\N{\rENG}Godmother.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.47,1:30:09.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,為了藍蝶仙子\N{\rENG}For Flittle!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.43,1:30:18.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,抓到她了\N{\rENG}We've got her!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.90,1:31:09.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,快跑  快跑\N{\rENG}Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.07,1:31:11.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,這邊  這邊\N{\rENG}This way! This way!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.78,1:31:12.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\rENG}Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.20,1:31:56.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,退下\N{\rENG}Stand down!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.04,1:32:00.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不想打這場仗\N{\rENG}This is not my fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.34,1:32:04.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,我母親想要戰爭  而你讓她如願以償\N{\rENG}My mother wanted a war, and you're giving it to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.17,1:32:08.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不會允許她的仇恨毀滅你我的王國\N{\rENG}I won't allow her hatred to ruin my kingdom or yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.88,1:32:29.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,我手上不會沾染仙子的血\N{\rENG}There will be no Fey blood on my hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.43,1:32:52.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,這邊  這邊\N{\rENG}This way! This way!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.50,1:32:56.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑪琳菲森回來了\N{\rENG}Maleficent's back!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.25,1:33:02.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,她要去找王后\N{\rENG}She's going for the queen.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.49,1:33:11.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,停手  停手\N{\rENG}Yield! Yield!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.71,1:33:12.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,停手\N{\rENG}Stand down!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.65,1:33:14.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,放下武器\N{\rENG}Lower your weapons!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.37,1:33:29.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,我跟他們預言的惡魔出現了\N{\rENG}There's the evil that I promised them.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.64,1:33:36.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們比人類還容易預測\N{\rENG}Your kind is more predictable than humans.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.03,1:33:42.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\rENG}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.95,1:33:44.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\rENG}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.87,1:33:47.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,大致如此\N{\rENG}Well, almost.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.39,1:33:48.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\rENG}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.64,1:33:51.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,很抱歉我懷疑了你  但你不是這樣的\N{\rENG}I'm sorry I doubted you, but this isn't you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.86,1:33:53.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,這不是唯一的方法\N{\rENG}There's another way.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.70,1:33:55.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,我瞭解你\N{\rENG}I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.56,1:33:58.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,我瞭解你\N{\rENG}I know you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.35,1:34:01.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不瞭解\N{\rENG}You do not.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.20,1:34:05.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,我瞭解\N{\rENG}Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.98,1:34:08.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,你是我母親\N{\rENG}You're my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.94,1:34:46.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rENG}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.10,1:35:04.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,你知道偉大領袖的必備條件嗎  奧蘿拉\N{\rENG}Do you know what makes a great leader, Aurora?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.90,1:35:08.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,向子民灌輸恐懼的能力\N{\rENG}The ability to instill fear in your subjects...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.19,1:35:09.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,並且利用那種恐懼\N{\rENG}and then use that fear...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.66,1:35:10.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\rENG}Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.03,1:35:13.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,對付你的敵人\N{\rENG}against your enemies.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.78,1:35:15.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,所以...\N{\rENG}So...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.99,1:35:20.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,我散佈了那個關于邪惡女巫\N{\rENG}I spread the story of the evil witch...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.50,1:35:23.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,以及被她施咒的公主的故事\N{\rENG}and the princess she cursed.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.08,1:35:27.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,誰喚醒了睡美人並不重要\N{\rENG}It didn't matter who woke Sleeping Beauty.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.91,1:35:30.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們都嚇壞了\N{\rENG}They were all terrified.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.85,1:35:34.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,而故事成為了傳說\N{\rENG}And the story became legend.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.50,1:35:38.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道你認為我是惡魔\N{\rENG}I know you think I'm a monster.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.20,1:35:44.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,但我對國王  瑪琳菲森和我兒子所做的\N{\rENG}But what I did to the king, to Maleficent, to my son...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.72,1:35:47.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,都是為了奧斯戴王國\N{\rENG}I did for Ulstead.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.94,1:35:50.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,你背叛了你的同類\N{\rENG}You are a traitor to your kind,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.51,1:35:52.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,你要為此付出代價\N{\rENG}and you will pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.46,1:35:55.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑪琳菲森已死\N{\rENG}Maleficent is dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.26,1:36:01.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們再也不會生活在恐懼之中了\N{\rENG}We will never again live in fear!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.95,1:36:03.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,回來\N{\rENG}Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.92,1:36:10.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,奧斯戴王國終于自由了\N{\rENG}Ulstead is free at last!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.63,1:36:11.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,放開我\N{\rENG}Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.06,1:36:22.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事\N{\rENG}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.78,1:39:49.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,看啊\N{\rENG}Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.53,1:39:52.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,你好  小怪物\N{\rENG}Hello, Beasty.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.37,1:40:12.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想你了\N{\rENG}I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.04,1:40:15.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,你撞到腦袋了嗎\N{\rENG}Did you bump your head, then?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.14,1:40:17.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,對\N{\rENG}I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.29,1:40:21.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,菲力浦\N{\rENG}Philip.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.04,1:40:23.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\rENG}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.29,1:40:27.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,你愛我女兒嗎\N{\rENG}Do you love my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.17,1:40:31.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,全心全意\N{\rENG}With everything I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.77,1:40:41.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,那好\N{\rENG}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.49,1:40:54.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想這個是你的\N{\rENG}I believe this belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.59,1:41:02.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,詛咒是無法結束的\N{\rENG}Curses don't end.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.70,1:41:04.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,只能被解開\N{\rENG}They're broken.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.83,1:41:30.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,結束了\N{\rENG}It ends.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.68,1:41:39.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,不會再有戰爭了\N{\rENG}There will be no more fighting.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.00,1:41:42.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,奧斯戴再也不會進攻摩爾了\N{\rENG}Ulstead will never attack the Moors again.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.73,1:41:44.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,從今日起\N{\rENG}And from this day on...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.74,1:41:46.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們攜手向前\N{\rENG}we move forward...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.35,1:41:48.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,找到前行的道路\N{\rENG}and find our way...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.12,1:41:52.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,共用和平\N{\rENG}in peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.86,1:41:53.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,團結一致\N{\rENG}Together.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.70,1:42:00.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,今天  會有一場婚禮\N{\rENG}Today, there will be a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.48,1:42:02.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,這不只是兩個人的結合\N{\rENG}Not just a union of two people...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.96,1:42:06.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,更是兩個王國的結合\N{\rENG}but a union of two kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.09,1:42:09.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,所有人都受邀參加\N{\rENG}And all are invited...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.74,1:42:11.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,所有人都是安全的\N{\rENG}all are safe...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.95,1:42:14.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,所有人都將受到歡迎\N{\rENG}and all are welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.61,1:42:50.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,你好呀\N{\rENG}Hello, there.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.86,1:43:34.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們不能和怪物生活在一起...\N{\rENG}We cannot live amongst monsters...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.27,1:43:42.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,某人真該把那對角好好藏起來\N{\rENG}Someone should really cover those horns.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.63,1:44:01.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,要是康諾爾能看見你就好了\N{\rENG}If only Conall could see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.49,1:44:04.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,博拉\N{\rENG}Borra...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.00,1:44:08.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,是時候回家了\N{\rENG}it's time to come home.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.51,1:44:16.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們好\N{\rENG}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.39,1:44:19.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,你能過來一下嗎\N{\rENG}Can you come here?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.81,1:44:31.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,怎麼了\N{\rENG}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.79,1:44:35.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,你願意把我送出去嗎\N{\rENG}Will you give me away?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.07,1:44:37.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,絕不\N{\rENG}Never.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.59,1:44:39.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.52,1:44:42.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,你願意送我出嫁嗎\N{\rENG}Will you walk me down the aisle?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.06,1:44:48.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,願意\N{\rENG}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.18,1:45:13.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,向所有今天被我傷到的人道歉\N{\rENG}Apologies to anyone I might have mauled today.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.90,1:45:26.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,那是...\N{\rENG}Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.38,1:45:28.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,她能把她變回去的\N{\rENG}She can change her back.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.25,1:45:31.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,應該能\N{\rENG}I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.44,1:45:33.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,得我們願意才行\N{\rENG}Only if we wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.78,1:45:36.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,父親\N{\rENG}Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.73,1:45:43.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,很高興見到你\N{\rENG}I'm so glad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.22,1:45:46.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,我一直夢想著這一刻\N{\rENG}I've dreamed of this moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.36,1:45:49.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,兩個王國終於團結一致\N{\rENG}Two kingdoms united at last.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.26,1:45:51.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,而這都多虧了你\N{\rENG}And it's because of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.28,1:45:54.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,我太為你感到驕傲了  太驕傲了\N{\rENG}I'm so proud of you. So proud.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.04,1:46:25.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,她穿綠色更好看\N{\rENG}She looks better in green.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.62,1:46:27.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,你是說粉色吧\N{\rENG}Pink, you mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.50,1:46:31.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,不  綠色\N{\rENG}No, in green.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.87,1:46:32.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,粉色\N{\rENG}Pink.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.68,1:46:34.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,-綠色  -粉色\N{\rENG}- Green. - Pink.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.30,1:46:38.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,藍蝶仙子\N{\rENG}Flittle!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.85,1:46:40.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,太完美了\N{\rENG}It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.49,1:47:26.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,放手吧\N{\rENG}Let her go.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.80,1:47:42.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,你振作一點\N{\rENG}Pull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.50,1:47:46.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們在此聯合兩個王國\N{\rENG}We are here to join two kingdoms...
